ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次見佢地既單上羅湖搵<br />\n<br />\n如果散光過三百同加埋水腳<br />\n<br />\n其實同香港差唔多🤣<br />\n<br />\n我仲要攞副OP 上去配(日本買)<br />\n<br />\n諗起都驚驚地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後都係香港再配, 因為塊鏡度數唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0795162073168b005d587d52a7c5ddefe5b049a0","tid":596111,"uid":72827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:39:56.000Z","msg":"收檔啦"}]}